{"tid":1433160,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣一芳推「買大送中」優惠","createTime":"2019-08-08T12:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:54:14.000Z","uid":62958,"like":15,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dc10c3cbb5a89413077fa3da646e7c3976e595fb","tid":1433160,"uid":62958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"[新聞] 一芳推「買大送中」難抵怒火 1.9萬網友<br />\n<a href=\"https://moptt.tw/p/Gossiping.M.1565260163.A.438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoptt.tw%2Fp%2FGossiping.M.1565260163.A.438&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9WAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=ecdaa848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://moptt.tw/p/Gossiping.M.1565260163.A.438</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8月1日起就推出「甘蔗系列」優惠活動，「8/1-9/8期間<span style=\"color: red;\">只要購買甘蔗系列飲品大杯，就送包種綠茶中杯</span>」，提前變調；網友至今仍在底下批評「一芳真的『紅』了耶！人爲財死吃相噁心 真的表現的淋漓盡致耶」、「哈囉！原本還蠻喜歡喝一芳的～現在決定抵制你們了！請你們去大陸設點吧。祝福你們生意興隆」、「台灣人拒喝台灣一芳水果茶」、「杯子請改名叫『一芳各表』」留言數已經達到1.9萬則。"},{"pid":"eed039ed5bf2411611d9ff10693b285f177535be","tid":1433160,"uid":205674,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:02:09.000Z","msg":"依家反送中 你仲要送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0154d0b35b57996b93dd786cf6435da9ed83ab","tid":1433160,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb27f7cb0273c9b05d5fd881eae9041162a4e469","tid":1433160,"uid":16790,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:45:56.000Z","msg":"仲要送中 明玩野"},{"pid":"34ee67402e974fd1b84347470019d527e350cbc1","tid":1433160,"uid":39182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一芳各表"},{"pid":"8dca630cf4c7572f8868f851b31e7190a60743c4","tid":1433160,"uid":144201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:51:02.00